{"tid":1057222,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真討論］有無人成日都唔知自己做緊咩？","createTime":"2019-03-11T17:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T08:16:53.000Z","uid":1044,"like":88,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"231b595c8d01e44ead1ca68894b61af5e085aa64","tid":1057222,"uid":1044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T17:31:38.000Z","msg":"我就係成日都唔知自己做緊咩。返學/做project/搵資料，個人嘅肉體就係度，但個腦就唔係諗緊當面做緊嘅嘢。跟住之後我想諗返呢段時間我諗緊啲咩，但我又諗唔出/忘記咗，攪到成日係度鳩吓鳩吓咁又幾個鐘，鳩多幾吓又一日，零生產力。<br />\n<br />\n依家做緊project又係咁，對住成份空白嘅嘢，唔知邊度入手/想寫啲咩，上網搵吓data，搵到咁上吓，問返自己搵咗啲咩data/啱唔啱用落去，結果自己又係答唔出。<br />\n<br />\n我都開始質疑自己嘅能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。明明以前都仲好啲，但近呢一兩年就變差。有無人都係同我咁？"},{"pid":"8835cc29f52dae90dc1131e480c10c028e1572cb","tid":1057222,"uid":1044,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T17:37:20.000Z","msg":"Btw我仲有對寫文恐懼，有埋data都好難落筆，係咁諗點樣explain，諗一句都諗好耐，諗諗吓又唔想諗，又諗咗其他嘢/腦袋空白鳩fing mode，攪到我寫一篇文要幾個鐘，甚至幾個鐘都係我幾句貨仔，又係生產能力整低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d523b0bbdecc221a356a3a04927edbba4fe9e01","tid":1057222,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T17:48:55.000Z","msg":"生產力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba9051649d73197926ccdab67a0e61dc337e6bf","tid":1057222,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T17:53:37.000Z","msg":"are you robot?"},{"pid":"494f376fecb39790d3ea869bd22ef353376fb9af","tid":1057222,"uid":1044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d523b0bbdecc221a356a3a04927edbba4fe9e01","tid":1057222,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T17:48:55.000Z","msg":"生產力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T22:57:04.000Z","msg":"我語